Creating application web using REACT and CREATE-REACT-APP


1 - step
open Terminal on computer and write:

  npm install react
  
2 - step
Install "CREATE REACT APP" for creating the React folder in your computer
open Terminal on computer and write:

  npm install -g create-react-app

3 - step 
Then for create the React folder using CREATE-REACT-APP write on Terminal:

  create-react-app init-project
  
  cd init-project
  
  npm start
